OL,3,CExtreme wildfire warning issued
OL,5,FAn extreme wildfire warning has been
OL,6,Fissued across southern Scotland - for
OL,7,Fthe fourth time this year - with high
OL,8,Ftemperatures and warm weather forecast
OL,9,Ffor the rest of this week.
OL,11,FThe wildfire danger assessment shows a
OL,12,F'very high' warning until 29 April, an
OL,13,F'extreme' warning from 30 April until
OL,14,F3 May and then levelling back down to
OL,15,F'very high' on 4 May.
OL,17,FIt's the second time this month a
OL,18,Fwildfire warning has been in place,
OL,19,Fwith firefighters responding to a
OL,20,Flarge blaze in the Galloway Hills on 5
OL,21,FApril 2025.
