OL,3,CExtreme wildfire warning issued
OL,5,FEarlier this month ITV Border reporter
OL,6,FKate Walby visited the land which is
OL,7,Fexpected to take ten years to recover.
OL,9,FBoth the Scottish Fire and Rescue
OL,10,FService and Scottish Wildfire Forum
OL,11,Furge the public to avoid lighting
OL,12,Ffires outdoors across all areas of
OL,13,FScotland.
OL,15,FThey say wildfires can threaten nearby
OL,16,Fcommunities, land and wildlife and
OL,17,Fburn for days.
