OL,3,CExtreme wildfire warning issued
OL,5,FArea Commander Michael Humphreys, from
OL,6,Fthe Scottish Fire and Rescue Service,
OL,7,Fsays many parts of Scotland are
OL,8,Fvulnerable and tinder dry, providing
OL,9,F"all the ingredients for fire to take
OL,10,Fhold and spread."
OL,12,FHe said: "We are asking the public to
OL,13,Fexercise extreme caution and avoid
OL,14,Fusing anything involving a naked flame.
OL,16,F"At this time of year in early Spring,
OL,17,Fwe typically have a large volume of
OL,18,Fdead, bone-dry vegetation across large
OL,19,Fareas of countryside. This essentially
OL,20,Facts as a fuel for fire.
