OL,3,CExtreme wildfire warning issued
OL,5,F"Many rural and remote communities are
OL,6,Fhugely impacted by wildfires, which
OL,7,Fcan cause significant damage.
OL,9,F"Livestock, farmland, wildlife,
OL,10,Fprotected woodland and sites of
OL,11,Fspecial scientific interest can all be
OL,12,Fdevastated by these fires - as can the
OL,13,Flives of people living and working in
OL,14,Frural communities.
OL,16,F"Human behaviour can significantly
OL,17,Flower the chance of a wildfire
OL,18,Fstarting, so it is imperative we all
OL,19,Fact responsibly while enjoying the
OL,20,Foutdoors especially over the coming
OL,21,Fdays of predicted sunshine.
