OL,3,CExtreme wildfire warning issued
OL,5,F"By following some simple but key
OL,6,Fadvice, we can significantly reduce
OL,7,Fthe risk of wildfire occurring."
OL,9,FAdvice issued by Cumbria's Fire and
OL,10,FRescue Service:
OL,12,FYou can do your bit to protect against
OL,13,Fwildfires by:
OL,15,F- Only have campfires and barbecues in
OL,16,Fallocated areas and always ensure that
OL,17,Fthey are fully extinguished.
OL,19,F- Never leave your open fire
OL,20,Funattended.
