OL,3,CExtreme wildfire warning issued
OL,5,F- Dispose of cigarettes and smoking
OL,6,Fmaterials safely.
OL,8,F- If you see a fire outdoors, move to
OL,9,Fa place of safety and report it by
OL,10,Fcalling 999 and do not attempt to
OL,11,Ftackle the fire yourself. Provide as
OL,12,Fmuch information such as the size of
OL,13,Fthe fire, location and terrain.
